            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Beatitudine <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> Constantis victoris <lb n="2"/>ac triumfatoris semper <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>provisa copia quae horreis deerat <lb n="4"/>postea quam condendis horrea deesse coeperunt <lb n="5"/>haec <expan><abbr>Vulc</abbr><ex>atius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Rufinus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praet</abbr><ex>orio</ex></expan> per se coepta <lb n="6"/>in securitatem perpet&amp;lt;ua=E&amp;gt;m rei annonariae dedicavit 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hedera in Z. 5. (B): Tóth: Z. 2: triumphatoris.</p>
            </div>
